 * @deprecated Use computeBlake3Hash (yakcc:b8c9d0e1) from @yakcc/atoms/computeBlake3Hash instead.
 * computeChecksum uses a djb2-variant that is not cryptographically secure.
 * Retained for backward compatibility only.
